headline: ER Services Earns Coveted Carrier Factory Authorized Dealer Designation
summary: ER Services has earned the Carrier Factory Authorized Dealer designation and is now recognized among the best dealers in the U.S. and Canada. Carrier is a part of Carrier Global Corporation (NYSE: CARR), global leader in intelligent climate and energy solutions.
